fter their kind, and the tree yielding fruit, whose seed was in itself, after its kind: and God saw that it was good.", :text=>"American King James Version"}, {:version=>"And the earth brought forth grass, and herb yielding seed after his kind, and the tree yielding fruit, whose seed was in itself, after his kind: and God saw that it was good.", :text=>"American Standard Version"}, {:version=>"And the earth brought forth grass, herbs yielding seed after their kind, and trees bearing fruit, wherein is the seed thereof, after their kind: and God saw that it was good.", :text=>"Brenton Septuagint Translation"}, {:version=>"And the earth brought forth the herb of grass bearing seed according to its kind and according to its likeness, and the fruit tree bearing fruit whose seed is in it, according to its kind on the earth, and God saw that it was good.", :text=>"Douay-Rheims Bible"}, {:version=>"And the earth brought forth the green herb, and such as yieldeth seed according to its kind, and the tree that beareth fruit having seed each one according to its kind. And God saw that it was good. ", :text=>"Darby Bible Translation"}, {:version=>"And the earth brought forth grass, herb producing seed after its kind, and trees yielding fruit, the seed of which is in them, after their kind. And God saw that it was good.", :text=>"English Revised Version"}, {:version=>"And the earth brought forth grass, herb yielding seed after its kind, and tree bearing fruit, wherein is the seed thereof, after its kind: and God saw that it was good.", :text=>"Webster's Bible Translation"}, {:version=>"And the earth brought forth grass, and herb yielding seed after its kind, and the tree yielding fruit, whose seed was in itself, after its kind: and God saw that it was good.", :text=>"World English Bible"}, {:version=>"The earth brought forth grass, herbs yielding seed after their kind, and trees bearing fruit, with its seed in it, after their kind; and God saw that it was good.", :text=>"Young's 